@startuml plugin-lifecycle

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

title jeeves-meta-openclaw — Plugin Lifecycle

participant "OpenClaw Gateway" as GW
participant "Plugin\nregister()" as Plugin
participant "@karmaniverous/jeeves\nComponentWriter" as Core
participant "jeeves-meta\nservice" as Service

== Startup ==

GW -> Plugin: register(api)
activate Plugin

Plugin -> Plugin: init({ workspacePath, configRoot })
Plugin -> Plugin: registerMetaTools(api, client)
note right: meta_list\nmeta_detail\nmeta_trigger\nmeta_preview

Plugin -> Core: createComponentWriter(component)
Plugin -> Core: writer.start()
deactivate Plugin

== Periodic Cycle (every 73s) ==

Core -> Service: GET /status
Service --> Core: StatusResponse

Core -> Service: GET /metas
Service --> Core: MetasResponse

Core -> Core: generateMetaMenu()\n→ TOOLS.md section

Core -> Core: updateManagedSection()\n→ write TOOLS.md

Core -> Core: refreshPlatformContent()\n→ SOUL.md / AGENTS.md

== Tool Invocation ==

GW -> Plugin: meta_trigger({ path })
Plugin -> Service: POST /synthesize
Service --> Plugin: { status: "accepted" }
Plugin --> GW: ToolResult

@enduml
